metadata.name: This Is NOT the Notre-Dame Cathedral
metadata.description:
She took some pictures,
other pictures and places formed in her mind,
they did not exist in the real world,
she tried to bring them to this world!

Dear visitors,
Please don't let reality devastate your imagination, even when you are recording facts!

This is my imagination while I'm photographing reality, so, this is NOT the Notre-Dame Cathedral in Paris!
